rows.label: qst000302_msg002
rows.name:
For a moment there I thought
it was all over, mo. Thank
you for saving me, mo.

rows.label: qst000302_msg003
rows.name: I'm so glad the cargo is safe, mo[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst000302_msg004
rows.name:
Mo? Are you curious
about the cargo, mo?

rows.label: qst000302_msg005
rows.name:
This is Puffoundation and
Treesap Conditioner, mo.

rows.label: qst000302_msg006
rows.name:
I was on my way to Torigo
to deliver these Gula-exclusive
cosmetics, mo.

rows.label: qst000302_msg007
rows.name:
If you hadn't come along, I would
have been monster food, mo.

rows.label: qst000302_msg008
rows.name:
Oh, right! As a thank you, I'll
sneak you a few items, mo.

rows.label: qst000302_msg009
rows.name:
To be honest, this is all Tunini
has to give right now, mo[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst000302_msg010
rows.name:
You really saved me, mo.
No, thank *you*, mo!
